{"tid":1970714,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"友情中最恐怖嘅就係你當人朋友，但人地無當過你係朋友","createTime":"2020-04-13T10:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T17:15:55.000Z","uid":325757,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8914ed9e4eacd9f50dd093f103b23b93b21ed9","tid":1970714,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無人明？你當人地係好朋友 但係人地唔當你係<br />\n可能有人會話朋友嘅嘢都係合則來不合則去嘅姐，而且無乜友誼真係可以keep一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係就算keep唔耐 最起碼嗰陣仲係朋友嘅時候大家都真心對大家 咁你話幾好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人因為受過傷所以變到好敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然已經走出大部份 但係識新朋友都係唔夠膽全情投入，有時又會因為一句說話唔開心，會不斷諗呢句嘢係互串定係真心講嘅呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cf712e68108fe88eb8da9933e73ecbf6b8ffa5","tid":1970714,"uid":122231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:11:29.000Z","msg":"我明<br />\n<br />\n所以我冇朋友"},{"pid":"4cd4b9be00909380458af70b63b59f9f6e6e9213","tid":1970714,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:19:42.000Z","msg":"同齡嘅人開始炒股講車買名牌，完全跟唔到<br />\n<br />\n         <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02154db4089554c9310487d4b87f011abbe9ab83","tid":1970714,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5cf712e68108f